
#### Content

- run_elemental-metals.py          --> input script to launch the ColourWorkflow (example for elemental metals)
- run_intermetallics.py            --> input script to launch the ColourWorkflow (example for binary compounds of gold)
- optical_constants.py             --> post-processing AiiDA script to calculate several optical constants, such as the reflectivity, and the colour coordinates starting from the dielectric function


